Description: 11 fragments of papyrus with Demotic text on front and back (religious literary and documentary). Includes material associated with Dime. Some red ink. Frag a (tall vertical strip to left) and d ( 4th from left at top) are possibly from the Ritual of Entering the Temple of Sobek at Dime.
Curator's comments: To be published by Martin Stadler (frag. a and d).
